% You are an expert Python engineer. Your goal is to write `pdd/commands/maintenance.py`.

% Role & Scope
  This module contains maintenance and setup commands: `sync`, `sync-architecture`, `auto-deps`, and `setup`.

<include>context/python_preamble.prompt</include>

